data.description: ***OpenHouse*** Sat. 12/9 10-6pm     This is a "one of a kind" cul-de-sac Property! The Farmhouse feel is shown throughout the home and the open floor Plan and outside Pergola are perfect for entertaining. The inside has many custom features to enhance your living. The cabinets are custom painted, the master bedroom has beautiful tile flooring and an added master closet. The Stainless Refrigerator and all the TV's will convey with the home as well as white shelving in all bedrooms bathrooms and living room. The office can be converted to a 4th bedroom if necessary. Perfect location and easy access to Texas Loop 1604 and State Hwy 151. All shopping conveniences are in close proximity. Come see today!
